OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FThe Great North Air Ambulance Service
OL,8,F(GNAAS) is trying to raise #2.5
OL,9,Fmillion to secure the deposit for what
OL,10,Fit describes as a "vital" third
OL,11,Fhelicopter.
OL,13,FThe deposits for two other new
OL,14,Fhelicopters have already been secured,
OL,15,Fto replace their existing aircraft.
OL,17,FGNAAS says the helicopters' age means
OL,18,Fthat maintenance costs are "ever-
OL,19,Frising", and part shortages mean the
OL,20,Faircraft need extended periods of
OL,21,Fdowntime.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FPhil Lambert, chief pilot, told ITV
OL,8,FBorder: "It's a very rural area we
OL,9,Flive in, and our patients depend on us
OL,10,Fto get there quickly, and then
OL,11,Ftransport them to a hospital as
OL,12,Fefficiently as possible.
OL,14,F"To put it into context, if someone
OL,15,Fneeds to go to a major trauma centre,
OL,16,Fparticularly on the West Coast of
OL,17,FCumbria, you're looking at an hour, an
OL,18,Fhour and a half. We can do that in
OL,19,Fless than half an hour.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,F"Not only that, we take the doctor and
OL,8,Fmedical team to the patient, so
OL,9,Fthey're there all the time with them.
OL,10,FSo it makes a huge difference."
OL,12,FThe Air Ambulance used to have three
OL,13,Fhelicopters, and it says returning to
OL,14,Fthis number will aid its response to
OL,15,Femergencies.
OL,17,FThe service has been operating for
OL,18,Fover 25 years, and covers an area of
OL,19,Faround 8 thousand square miles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FThis year alone it has been called out
OL,8,Fnearly 2,000.
OL,10,FCEO of GNAAS, Joe Garcia said:
OL,11,F"Helicopters being as complex as they
OL,12,Fare, we need to service and maintain
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"Those bigger services leave us in a
OL,16,Fposition where we're restricted - we
OL,17,Fcan't respond to two emergencies at
OL,18,Fthe same time. That's why it's
OL,19,Fessential that we have a third
OL,20,Faircraft."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FGNAAS' current aircraft are Dauphin N3
OL,8,Fand Dauphin N3+ helicopters, which
OL,9,Fhave responded to thousands of life-
OL,10,Fsaving missions over their lifetime.
OL,12,FTo meet rising demand for their
OL,13,Fservice, GNAAS has invested in three
OL,14,Fnew helicopters called Airbus H1455
OL,15,FD2, which the charity says are "state
OL,16,Fof the art".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1776359146
OL,3,CGreat North Air Ambulance Service
OL,4,Ctrying to raise #2.5million for new
OL,5,Chelicopter
OL,7,FPhil Lambert, chief pilot, said: "With
OL,8,Fonly two helicopters, we live on a
OL,9,Fknife-edge. If one is in maintenance
OL,10,Fand the other develops a fault, we're
OL,11,Fgrounded and that means we can't
OL,12,Fanswer a 999 call by helicopter."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
